Women’s Fashion at Burlington
Top names at sensational prices is what you’ll find when you shop at Burlington. Think incredible women’s clothing from brands you love and designers that wow. You can indulge your passion for fashion at a fraction of the cost of other retailers' prices.

Burlington has women’s fashions for everyone. Styles that are totally on-trend, like peasant blouses, maxi dresses, the latest in women’s denim and more. Or if you’re more of a timeless dresser, Burlington has the classics too. Shirt dresses, career pants for work, blouses, skirt suits and more. Burlington also carries an incredible selection of women’s plus size fashions and petite fashions too.

Heading out for the evening? Burlington has you covered. Special occasion dresses that sparkle and shimmer (but won’t blow your budget) plus women’s shoes and accessories to match so you’re guaranteed to create an outfit that dazzles. Or maybe your day calls for the gym and then errands? Check out our incredible selection of workout wear. We’ve got performance tops and pants that give you a stylish look in or out of the gym.

Work or play, make Burlington your women’s fashion headquarters and save.



















