					Full Description



Burlington Stores, Inc., incorporated on February 13, 2013, is a retailer of branded apparel. As of January 28, 2017, the Company operated 592 retail stores, inclusive of an Internet store, in 45 states and Puerto Rico. Its product categories include coats, women, men, juniors, girls, boys, shoes, handbags and accessories, beauty and fragrance, home and toys. The product categories for coats include women's coats and jackets, men's coats and jackets, juniors coats and jackets, girls coats and jackets, boy's coats and jackets, baby girl coats and jackets, and baby boy coats and jackets. The product categories for women include active wear, bottoms, coats and jackets, dresses, tops, scrubs, suit and suit separates, sweaters, swimwear and cover-ups. It also includes accessories, beauty and fragrance, handbags, jewelry, shoes and watches. The product categories for men include accessories, active wear, casual button down shirts, dress shirts, men's coats jackets, fleece, graphic tees, hoodies and sweatshirts, jeans, joggers, long sleeve, pajamas and robes, pants, polos, shorts, socks and underwear, suits and suit separates, sweaters, vests and swimwear.The product categories for juniors include bottoms, coats and jackets, dresses, jumpsuits and rompers, sweaters, swimwear and tops. The product categories for girls include active wear, backpacks and luggage, bottoms, capris, cardigans and shrugs, character tees, girls coats and jackets, communion, dresses, girls accessories, hoodies and sweatshirts, jeans, joggers, leggings, girls sets, shirts and blouses, shorts, skirts, girls sleepwear, socks and underwear, special occasion, sweaters and swimwear. The product categories for boys include boys' sets, boys' school uniforms, button down shirts, casual sets, character tees, boys' coats and jackets, dress wear, dress wear sets, dress pants, dress shirts, hoodies and sweatshirts, jeans, joggers, polo shirts, shorts and sleepwear. The women's shoes that the Company offers include boots, booties, comfort, flats, pumps and heels, rain boots, sandals and flip flops, sneakers and wedges. Men's shoes include boat, boots, dress, sneakers and wedges. Kids shoes include baby shoes, toddlers shoes, girl shoes and boys shoes. The handbags and accessories include backpacks, clutches, cross body, designer, hobos, leather, satchels, totes and wallets, jewelry and watches. It also offers other accessories, including exercise, hosiery, slippers and sunglasses. The beauty and fragrance products include perfume, cologne, make up, bath and body, and makeup bags.The Company's product offering for home category include bedding and bath, furniture, home decor, kitchen and dining, luggage, rugs, storage and organization, window treatments and hardware. Home decor includes accent furniture, wall art, window treatments, rugs lighting throw pillows, blankets and throws, storage furniture, mirrors, decorative bins and baskets, clocks, frames, and candles and scents. The product offering for kitchen and dining include appliances, bake ware, coffee and tea, cookware, cutlery, food storage, linens, storage tools and gadgets, trash cans, bar and wine, dinnerware, drink ware, flat ware and serve ware. The Company also offers toys.

